text: Ella Rose Emhoff (born May 29, 1999) is an American artist and fashion designer. She is the daughter of former U.S. second gentleman Doug Emhoff and stepdaughter of former U.S. vice president Kamala Harris. Emhoff designs jackets, hats, coats, and knitted shorts, which she sells from her Instagram account and her website. She also sells ceramics, paintings, and drawings from her website. In January 2021, Emhoff signed with IMG Models worldwide, an international modeling agency in New York City. ==References== ==Other websites== * * Category:1999 births Category:Living people Category:Models from Los Angeles Category:American fashion designers Category:Artists from Los Angeles Category:American painters Category:Businesspeople from Los Angeles Category:Kamala Harris Category:American LGBT rights activists
